verbose_text: Gogali et al. found that serum levels of E-cad were significantly elevated in patients with non small cell lung cancer (NSCLC) and small cell lung cancer (SCLC) compared with healthy controls, and serum soluble E-cad levels were correlated with presence of distant metastasis in patients with SCLC and NSCLC, suggesting that E-cad may have prognostic value [XREF_BIBR].
